{"tid":868792,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Marvel4 終於知道there are no other way點解","createTime":"2018-10-19T19:06:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T05:14:26.000Z","uid":197852,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"70544d280adbc9fc170147d26e8f46c392a3ef99","tid":868792,"uid":197852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T19:06:09.000Z","msg":"復4入面<br />\n美國隊長準備同thanos攬住死<br />\n但要有IM幫助<br />\n之後IM不斷講there must have other ways<br />\n隊長同IM講 there are no other way<br />\n之後IM醒起博士提過佢there are no other way<br />\n所以忍痛幫隊長攬抄<br />\n<br />\n上集變灰隊員暫不會出現(主要原因係佢地未做英雄例如博士，女巫），有啲復3前死左人物會出現，例如博士個師父<br />\n<br />\n因為回到過去紐約之戰，殺死thanos，IM心結打開翻，而隊長既死，都令IM退隱，同條女結婚，唔想再要條女擔心，但好多復1至復3之間既反派都因為回到過去而復活咗，而快銀,幻視呢類其間出現既人物會唔會出現就未知<br />\n有少少似xmen 回到過去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAntman因為係未來回到過去，所以有份出場"},{"pid":"8f55d2c2c45a9a4dffc9028c77d53967f1cb3f9b","tid":868792,"uid":54871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T19:07:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70575d925d512311862e706c826caebcace2b92f","tid":868792,"uid":36432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T19:15:13.000Z","msg":"無鷹眼，零分"},{"pid":"0cd7899da89b50fb41442dbb6615fcaa98713802","tid":868792,"uid":79303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T19:49:03.000Z","msg":"石又無<br />\nCaptain Marvel 又無<br />\n唔明美國隊長有咩資格同人攬炒"},{"pid":"9fc5758895cbabb1495fb09e92c4a0ddf81788e0","tid":868792,"uid":43173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0cd7899da89b50fb41442dbb6615fcaa98713802","tid":868792,"uid":79303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T19:49:03.000Z","msg":"石又無<br />\nCaptain Marvel 又無<br />\n唔明美國隊長有咩資格同人攬炒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T20:12:48.000Z","msg":"咪係，滑嘟嘟唔出石都打贏Hulk"},{"pid":"6124890651879614c5be650266624ec67706dfa4","tid":868792,"uid":197852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fc5758895cbabb1495fb09e92c4a0ddf81788e0","tid":868792,"uid":43173,"like":1,"dis